<h2 class="bold font-l">Persona 5 Royal: Violet</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
In Persona 5 and its Updated Re-release, Persona 5 Royal, battle animations feature stylish character portrait cut-ins whenever a party member lands a Critical Hit or successfully exploits an enemy's elemental weakness. Character portraits for the player's currently active party members also appear when using an All-Out Attack, and a celebratory art splash additionally appears should an All-Out Attack end a battle. This video shows the portraits and All-Out Attack art used for &quot;Kasumi&quot;/Sumire Yoshizawa (codename: Violet), a party member exclusive to Royal's post-game story arc. </p>
</div>
<div class="video-examples-thumbs">
<a href="#video-link" data-video-id="2lylmp" data-video-descrip="In Super Smash Bros. Ultimate, Final Smashes are powerful, exclusive moves that can be unleashed by playable fighters while under certain circumstances, such as after breaking a Smash Ball item. To punctate their power, a cut-in of the fighter's UI portrait will appear on the screen when they perform their Final Smash.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Joker's Final Smash is the All-Out Attack, which is taken directly from his game of origin, Persona 5, complete with additional character portraits that appear for Joker and his fellow Phantom Thieves when the attack is performed.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;(Footage courtesy of TheBassSinger from YouTube)" data-video-title="Joker's Final Smash" data-video-url="https://d1w6li7s85ibls.cloudfront.net/qvbr/2lylmp_640x360p_qvbr.mp4" data-video-thumbnail="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/427a607a_b5a5_44cb_80d7_bb6a5dca45da.jpeg" data-video-trope="Main/SuperMovePortraitAttack" data-video-tropename="Super Move Portrait Attack" data-video-approval="APPROVED" data-video-troper-rating="" data-video-average-rating="" data-video-rating-count="" data-video-media-sources="VideoGame/SuperSmashBros,VideoGame/Persona5,VideoGame/SuperSmashBrosUltimate,VideoGame/Persona5Royal" class="video-launch-link video-overlay-link video-background-image lazy-image" data-src="https://static.tvtropes.org/trope_videos_transcoded/images/sd/427a607a_b5a5_44cb_80d7_bb6a5dca45da.jpeg">
<p><span class="bold">Joker's Final S...</span></p>
</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
